#We-Split APP :D 

This is a simple addition that will make your life much easier. We-Split is an application that splits your bill among your friends and also calculates the total bill amount, including the tip if you select a percentage. The app's interface is very simple, but simplicity is often the best approach. In the future, the application I create will be much more advanced.

